text:
I love how Chaeyoung’s not overpowering Yeonjun to make him shine more. Tho it’s a short clip, you’ll see how appreciative the girls are with this kind of collabs.

I just noticed that Chaeyoung unlike their stage performances doesn’t extend much her arms nor legs (even the flicks) on this clip that Yeonjun on the other hand slayyed. That’s why I said not overpowering the guy to make him shine more because I feel like Chaeyoung did it intentional. And Yeonjun really did shine even if those were short and simple.

I’m not hating anyone here so please stop. I just love how the girls appreciate their collabs. Geez.
